business_definition: Group item containing common variables for DB2 database operations and error handling
Display format for DB2 SQLCODE return value used for error checking and reporting
Dummy integer field for DB2 processing initialization (USAGE COMP-3) (VALUE 0)
Flag indicating the status of DB2 processing operations
Condition indicating successful DB2 operation completion (VALUE '0')
Condition indicating DB2 operation encountered an error (VALUE '1')
Description of the current DB2 action being performed for logging and error reporting (VALUE SPACES)
Group item for formatting DB2 DSNTIAC utility messages
Length of the DSNTIAC formatted message text (USAGE COMP) (VALUE +720)
Container for formatted DSNTIAC message text lines
Individual line of DSNTIAC formatted message text (OCCURS 10) (VALUE SPACES)
Logical record length for DSNTIAC message processing (USAGE COMP) (VALUE +72)
Group item for DSNTIAC error message construction
DSNTIAC error message prefix identifier (VALUE 'DSNTIAC CD')
Error code in character format (VALUE SPACES)
Error code in numeric format (REDEFINES WS-DSNTIAC-ERR-CD-X)
